"""adingest — project-agnostic CLI for the ad-ingest service.

NO imports of ``ad_ingest.*`` — HTTP only. Three subcommands (``ingest``,
``range``, ``status``) render the 9-counter wire contract (5 row + 4 GA4)
per source through an 8-category verdict classifier as a ``rich`` table.
"""
